        "â€¢ **Challenges**: Encounter a variety of tasks that test your skills in different aspects of Old School RuneScape.\n"
        "â€¢ **Bonuses**: Land on special tiles that offer rewards or opportunities to hinder your opponents.\n"
        "â€¢ **Competition**: Race against other teams to see who can navigate the board and complete all tasks first.\n"
        "\n"
        "Are you ready to roll the dice and lead your team to victory? Let the games begin!"
